subject: Track and Field
Olympic Games (2008)
Awards, Decorations and Honors
lead_paragraph: The Jamaican sprinter Usain Bolt and the Russian pole-vaulter Yelena Isinbayeva won the World Athlete of the Year awards given by the I.A.A.F., track and field’s world governing body.
